title: Skinny S'mores Cupcakes
directions: Mix together entire box of cake and diet soda until well combined.
Spoon the cupcake mixture evenly into 24 cupcake tins.
Bake at 375 for 18 minutes or until a tooth pick comes out clean. Let cool for 10 to 15 minutes.
In a stand mixer, beat the cool whip and marshmallow fluff until well combined.
Fill a piping bag with the frosting mixture and pipe the frosting onto the cupcake. About two tablespoons of the frosting.
Crush the graham crackers in a zip lock bag with a rolling pin. Dip the cupcake onto the graham cracker crumbs. Top with graham piece (optional)
ingredients: 1 15 oz package of German Chocolate Cake mix or Devil's Food
